cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with intrusion detection and compensation in Cyber-Physical Systems (CPSs), which are vulnerable to cyber attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves system identification and control design, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The use of ARX identifier and MATLAB Simulink environment suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the design of a new controller, which may fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
